This repository builds and redistributes binary artifact images for the
PHP grpc extension from the PECL grpc package.

The grpc extension is part of the upstream gRPC project.

PECL package: https://pecl.php.net/package/grpc
Upstream source: https://github.com/grpc/grpc
Upstream license: Apache License 2.0

